A mysterious fire has destroyed a dormitory at Oloormirani High School in Narok West Sub-County.
Students lost their personal effects and bedding in the inferno, which started at 7pm on Sunday.
The students had gone for evening preps when the fire broke out. Firefighters from Narok Town arrived an hour after the students, staff and locals had put out the inferno.



